  <brief_title>Autologous Bone Marrow Transplantation in Acute Non-Lymphoblastic Leukemia During First or Subsequent Remission</brief_title>
  <official_title>Autologous Bone Marrow Transplantation for Acute Non-Lymphoblastic Leukemia During First or Subsequent Remission</official_title>
