  <source>Stanford University</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Evaluate the role of high dose chemotherapy with autologous hematopoietic cell
      transplantation for AML.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To use high dose chemotherapy with autologous stem cell rescue to try to increase the chance
      of long term control and cure of the disease.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
